- To install this module you need to install:
     + eBox components
        libebox
        ebox
     + Debian packages
	dhcp3-client
        iproute
        vlan
     + VLAN (801.q) enabled linux kernel

- Once all dependencies are satisfied, type:
	
	./configure
	make install

  configure will autodetect eBox base path to install

- Update your /etc/sudoers file with the ebox-sudoers command.

- You can import your current network configuration into eBox
using ebox-netcfg-import
